hejiang\"}, {\"begin\": 445, \"end\": 450, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999932897481, \"rank\": 6.709656250627792e-09, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Johannes Eisele\", \"from\": 370, \"to\": 385}, {\"ngram\": \"a sprawling 4 million square metre complex housing\", \"from\": 454, \"to\": 504}, {\"ngram\": \"more than 75,000 shops\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 527}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the2024 Paris Olympicsapproach, it has been a hive of international trade, with merchants rushing to fulfil Olympic-related orders.\", \"from\": 530, \"to\": 664, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 541, \"end\": 546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9442407042312614e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the2024\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 540}, {\"ngram\": \"a hive\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 583}, {\"ngram\": \"international trade\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 606}, {\"ngram\": \"merchants\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 622}, {\"ngram\": \"fulfil Olympic-related orders\", \"from\": 634, \"to\": 663}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The market is currently abuzz with French-themed products catering to the Olympic fever.\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 754, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The market\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 676}, {\"ngram\": \"French-themed products\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 723}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic fever\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 753}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yiwu's exports to France soared by 42 per cent in the first two months of 2024 compared to the previous year, reaching nearly \\u20ac75 million (US$81.5 million).\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 911, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 773, \"end\": 779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999971162320179, \"rank\": 2.8454341175021676e-06, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Yiwu's exports\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 769}, {\"ngram\": \"42 per cent\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 801}, {\"ngram\": \"the first two months\", \"from\": 805, \"to\": 825}, {\"ngram\": \"the previous year\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 863}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports goods exports surged by 70 per cent.\", \"from\": 912, \"to\": 955, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sports goods exports\", \"from\": 912, \"to\": 932}, {\"ngram\": \"cent\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 954}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This reflectsChina's robust manufacturing capabilitiesand pivotal role in global supply chains.\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 1051, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This reflectsChina's robust manufacturing capabilitiesand pivotal role\", \"from\": 956, \"to\": 1026}, {\"ngram\": \"global supply chains\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1050}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most products traded in Yiwu's market belong to labour-intensive light industries, such as textiles and consumer goods manufacturing.\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1186, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1077, \"end\": 1081, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yiwu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.606708893090605e-38, \"text\": \"Yiwu\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yiwu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yiwu\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Most products\", \"from\": 1053, \"to\": 1066}, {\"ngram\": \"labour-intensive light industries\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1134}, {\"ngram\": \"textiles\", \"from\": 1144, \"to\": 1152}, {\"ngram\": \"consumer goods\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1171}, {\"ngram\": \"manufacturing\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1185}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2023, these products accounted for over 40 per cent of Yiwu's export value and 52 per cent of its export growth.\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1302, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1245, \"end\": 1249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yiwu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.606708893090605e-38, \"text\": \"Yiwu\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yiwu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yiwu\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these products\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1210}, {\"ngram\": \"over 40 per cent\", \"from\": 1225, \"to\": 1241}, {\"ngram\": \"52 per cent\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1280}, {\"ngram\": \"its export growth\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1301}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite global supply chains shifting towards countries like Vietnam, the share of labour-intensive goods in China's total exports has only slightly decreased, from 18 per cent in late 2017 to 17 per cent in 2023.\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1517, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1365, \"end\": 1372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"score\": 0.9999978357296414, \"rank\": 2.1642620705219345e-06, \"text\": \"Vietnam\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnam\"}, {\"begin\": 1413, \"end\": 1418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999932897481, \"rank\": 6.709656250627792e-09, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"global supply chains\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1332}, {\"ngram\": \"countries\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1359}, {\"ngram\": \"the share\", \"from\": 1374, \"to\": 1383}, {\"ngram\": \"labour-intensive goods\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1409}, {\"ngram\": \"18 per cent\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1480}, {\"ngram\": \"17 per cent\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1508}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yiwu's robust production performance reflects China's broader shift from real estate to manufacturing investment.\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1632, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1565, \"end\": 1570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999932897481, \"rank\": 6.709656250627792e-09, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Yiwu's robust production performance\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1555}, {\"ngram\": \"real estate\", \"from\": 1592, \"to\": 1603}, {\"ngram\": \"manufacturing investment\", \"from\": 1607, \"to\": 1631}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the first quarter of 2024, China's industrial production rose by 6.1 per cent and manufacturing investment increased by nearly 10 per cent against a 5.3 per cent GDP growth rate.\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1814, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1663, \"end\": 1668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999932897481, \"rank\": 6.709656250627792e-09, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first quarter\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1653}, {\"ngram\": \"6.1 per cent and manufacturing investment\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1742}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly 10 per cent\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1774}, {\"ngram\": \"a 5.3 per cent GDP growth rate\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1813}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While China delivers affordable products globally, overcapacity has increased geopolitical risks and trade tensions, highlighted by Xi Jinping's recent European trip, aimed at mitigating these tensions.\", \"from\": 1816, \"to\": 2018, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1822, \"end\": 1827, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999932897481, \"rank\": 6.709656250627792e-09, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1948, \"end\": 1958, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xi_Jinping\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Xi Jinping\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xi_Jinping\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xi_Jinping\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"affordable products\", \"from\": 1837, \"to\": 1856}, {\"ngram\": \"overcapacity\", \"from\": 1867, \"to\": 1879}, {\"ngram\": \"geopolitical risks\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1912}, {\"ngram\": \"trade tensions\", \"from\": 1917, \"to\": 1931}, {\"ngram\": \"these tensions\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2017}]}, {\"sentence\": \"China's industrial utilisation ratio dipped below 75 per cent in early 2024, the lowest since 2016 - excluding 2020 at the outbreak of COVID-19 - revealing potential resource waste.\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2200, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2019, \"end\": 2024, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999932897481, \"rank\": 6.709656250627792e-09, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"75 per cent\", \"from\": 2069, \"to\": 2080}, {\"ngram\": \"the outbreak\", \"from\": 2138, \"to\": 2150}, {\"ngram\": \"COVID-19 - revealing potential resource waste\", \"from\": 2154, \"to\": 2199}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yiwu's export resilience is fuelled not just by its low-cost products but also by a sophisticated network of information exchanges and collaborative production across enterprise boundaries.\", \"from\": 2202, \"to\": 2391, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Yiwu's export resilience\", \"from\": 2202, \"to\": 2226}, {\"ngram\": \"its low-cost products\", \"from\": 2250, \"to\": 2271}, {\"ngram\": \"a sophisticated network\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2307}, {\"ngram\": \"information exchanges\", \"from\": 2311, \"to\": 2332}, {\"ngram\": \"collaborative production\", \"from\": 2337, \"to\": 2361}, {\"ngram\": \"enterprise boundaries\", \"from\": 2369, \"to\": 2390}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Its rapid production and delivery capabilities allow it to handle small orders efficiently.\", \"from\": 2392, \"to\": 2483, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Its rapid production and delivery capabilities\", \"from\": 2392, \"to\": 2438}, {\"ngram\": \"small orders\", \"from\": 2458, \"to\": 2470}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This flexibility starkly contrasts with large manufacturers, which rely on highly organised, large-scale production.\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2600, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This flexibility\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2500}, {\"ngram\": \"large manufacturers\", \"from\": 2524, \"to\": 2543}, {\"ngram\": \"highly organised, large-scale production\", \"from\": 2559, \"to\": 2599}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the nexus for foreign buyers and a wide range of suppliers, mainly small- and medium-sized enterprises, Yiwu demonstrates unique organisational skills that enable quick and cost-effective production tailored to specific orders.\", \"from\": 2602, \"to\": 2832, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2709, \"end\": 2713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yiwu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.606708893090605e-38, \"text\": \"Yiwu\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yiwu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yiwu\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the nexus\", \"from\": 2605, \"to\": 2614}, {\"ngram\": \"foreign buyers\", \"from\": 2619, \"to\": 2633}, {\"ngram\": \"a wide range\", \"from\": 2638, \"to\": 2650}, {\"ngram\": \"suppliers\", \"from\": 2654, \"to\": 2663}, {\"ngram\": \"unique organisational skills\", \"from\": 2727, \"to\": 2755}, {\"ngram\": \"quick and cost-effective production\", \"from\": 2768, \"to\": 2803}, {\"ngram\": \"specific orders\", \"from\": 2816, \"to\": 2831}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yiwu's production and delivery capabilities are anchored in its extensive industrial clusters, which foster both cooperation and competition among closely located enterprises.\", \"from\": 2834, \"to\": 3009, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Yiwu's production and delivery capabilities\", \"from\": 2834, \"to\": 2877}, {\"ngram\": \"its extensive industrial clusters\", \"from\": 2894, \"to\": 2927}, {\"ngram\": \"both cooperation\", \"from\": 2942, \"to\": 2958}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 2963, \"to\": 2974}, {\"ngram\": \"closely located enterprises\", \"from\": 2981, \"to\": 3008}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These clusters are organised around Yiwu's 78 industrial parks, which are home to over 4,500 small and medium enterprises (SMEs).\", \"from\": 3010, \"to\": 3139, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3046, \"end\": 3050, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yiwu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.606708893090605e-38, \"text\": \"Yiwu\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yiwu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yiwu\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These clusters\", \"from\": 3010, \"to\": 3024}, {\"ngram\": \"over 4,500 small and medium enterprises\", \"from\": 3092, \"to\": 3131}, {\"ngram\": \"SMEs\", \"from\": 3133, \"to\": 3137}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These SMEs are bolstered by the local government provisions of digital tools, flexible production technologies and support services, complemented by the application of production standards by industrial associations.\", \"from\": 3140, \"to\": 3356, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"These SMEs\", \"from\": 3140, \"to\": 3150}, {\"ngram\": \"the local government provisions\", \"from\": 3168, \"to\": 3199}, {\"ngram\": \"digital tools\", \"from\": 3203, \"to\": 3216}, {\"ngram\": \"flexible production technologies\", \"from\": 3218, \"to\": 3250}, {\"ngram\": \"support services\", \"from\": 3255, \"to\": 3271}, {\"ngram\": \"the application\", \"from\": 3289, \"to\": 3304}, {\"ngram\": \"production standards\", \"from\": 3308, \"to\": 3328}, {\"ngram\": \"industrial associations\", \"from\": 3332, \"to\": 3355}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yiwu demonstrates China's capacity for large-scale collaborative production involving multi-layered supply chains.\", \"from\": 3358, \"to\": 3472, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3376, \"end\": 3381, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999932897481, \"rank\": 6.709656250627792e-09, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Yiwu\", \"from\": 3358, \"to\": 3362}, {\"ngram\": \"large-scale collaborative production\", \"from\": 3397, \"to\": 3433}, {\"ngram\": \"multi-layered supply chains\", \"from\": 3444, \"to\": 3471}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Though export revenues from products like lighters may seem modest, their production is underpinned by complex supply chains incorporating over 30 components, including materials, precision moulds and electrical automation.\", \"from\": 3473, \"to\": 3696, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"export revenues\", \"from\": 3480, \"to\": 3495}, {\"ngram\": \"products\", \"from\": 3501, \"to\": 3509}, {\"ngram\": \"lighters\", \"from\": 3515, \"to\": 3523}, {\"ngram\": \"their production\", \"from\": 3541, \"to\": 3557}, {\"ngram\": \"complex supply chains\", \"from\": 3576, \"to\": 3597}, {\"ngram\": \"over 30 components\", \"from\": 3612, \"to\": 3630}, {\"ngram\": \"materials\", \"from\": 3642, \"to\": 3651}, {\"ngram\": \"precision moulds\", \"from\": 3653, \"to\": 3669}, {\"ngram\": \"electrical automation\", \"from\": 3674, \"to\": 3695}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With rising labour and material costs, maintaining cost competitiveness requires innovation.\", \"from\": 3697, \"to\": 3789, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"rising labour and material costs\", \"from\": 3702, \"to\": 3734}, {\"ngram\": \"cost competitiveness\", \"from\": 3748, \"to\": 3768}, {\"ngram\": \"innovation\", \"from\": 3778, \"to\": 3788}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This necessitates not only high-precision machine tools but also robust coordination to meet diverse production and safety standards.\", \"from\": 3790, \"to\": 3923, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"not only high-precision machine tools\", \"from\": 3808, \"to\": 3845}, {\"ngram\": \"robust coordination\", \"from\": 3855, \"to\": 3874}, {\"ngram\": \"diverse production and safety standards\", \"from\": 3883, \"to\": 3922}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Large-scale co-production also has application in other industries.\", \"from\": 3925, \"to\": 3992, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Large-scale co\", \"from\": 3925, \"to\": 3939}, {\"ngram\": \"production\", \"from\": 3940, \"to\": 3950}, {\"ngram\": \"application\", \"from\": 3960, \"to\": 3971}, {\"ngram\": \"other industries\", \"from\": 3975, \"to\": 3991}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Companies like SHEIN, an emerging fast fashion brand, have revolutionised the sector, outpacing traditional players like Zara.\", \"from\": 3993, \"to\": 4119, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4114, \"end\": 4118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zadar\", \"score\": 0.9999999757028494, \"rank\": 2.4297169716193793e-08, \"text\": \"Zara\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zadar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zadar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Companies\", \"from\": 3993, \"to\": 4002}, {\"ngram\": \"SHEIN\", \"from\": 4008, \"to\": 4013}, {\"ngram\": \"an emerging fast fashion brand\", \"from\": 4015, \"to\": 4045}, {\"ngram\": \"the sector\", \"from\": 4067, \"to\": 4077}, {\"ngram\": \"traditional players\", \"from\": 4089, \"to\": 4108}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unlike Zara, which relies on in-house production, SHEIN depends on thousands of SMEs and organises a flexible \\\"small-batch\\\" production approach that caters to rapid product design, manufacturing and delivery.\", \"from\": 4121, \"to\": 4329, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4128, \"end\": 4132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zadar\", \"score\": 0.9999999757028494, \"rank\": 2.4297169716193793e-08, \"text\": \"Zara\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zadar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zadar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"house\", \"from\": 4153, \"to\": 4158}, {\"ngram\": \"SHEIN\", \"from\": 4171, \"to\": 4176}, {\"ngram\": \"thousands\", \"from\": 4188, \"to\": 4197}, {\"ngram\": \"SMEs\", \"from\": 4201, \"to\": 4205}, {\"ngram\": \"a flexible \\\"small-batch\\\" production approach\", \"from\": 4220, \"to\": 4264}, {\"ngram\": \"rapid product design\", \"from\": 4280, \"to\": 4300}, {\"ngram\": \"manufacturing\", \"from\": 4302, \"to\": 4315}, {\"ngram\": \"delivery\", \"from\": 4320, \"to\": 4328}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By harnessing big data and AI algorithms, SHEIN quickly adapts to market trends.\", \"from\": 4331, \"to\": 4411, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4358, \"end\": 4360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.6575512406183536e-24, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"big data\", \"from\": 4345, \"to\": 4353}, {\"ngram\": \"SHEIN\", \"from\": 4373, \"to\": 4378}, {\"ngram\": \"market trends\", \"from\": 4397, \"to\": 4410}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SHEIN introduces between 700 and 1,000 new products daily, and updates around 50,000 new items weekly, compared to Zara - which introduces 25,000 new products annually.\", \"from\": 4412, \"to\": 4580, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4527, \"end\": 4531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zadar\", \"score\": 0.9999999757028494, \"rank\": 2.4297169716193793e-08, \"text\": \"Zara\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zadar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zadar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"SHEIN\", \"from\": 4412, \"to\": 4417}, {\"ngram\": \"between 700 and 1,000 new products\", \"from\": 4429, \"to\": 4463}, {\"ngram\": \"around 50,000 new items\", \"from\": 4483, \"to\": 4506}, {\"ngram\": \"25,000 new products\", \"from\": 4551, \"to\": 4570}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While China's industrial prowess benefits global consumers by providing affordable products such as clothing, electronics and smartphones, it is also a double-edged sword.\", \"from\": 4582, \"to\": 4753, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4588, \"end\": 4593, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999932897481, \"rank\": 6.709656250627792e-09, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"global consumers\", \"from\": 4624, \"to\": 4640}, {\"ngram\": \"affordable products\", \"from\": 4654, \"to\": 4673}, {\"ngram\": \"clothing\", \"from\": 4682, \"to\": 4690}, {\"ngram\": \"electronics\", \"from\": 4692, \"to\": 4703}, {\"ngram\": \"smartphones\", \"from\": 4708, \"to\": 4719}, {\"ngram\": \"a double-edged sword\", \"from\": 4732, \"to\": 4752}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Overcapacity has not only stirred geopolitical risk for Chinese manufacturers but also escalatedtrade tensions.\", \"from\": 4755, \"to\": 4866, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4811, \"end\": 4818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999992898358662, \"rank\": 7.100668850017397e-07, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Overcapacity\", \"from\": 4755, \"to\": 4767}, {\"ngram\": \"geopolitical risk\", \"from\": 4789, \"to\": 4806}, {\"ngram\": \"tensions\", \"from\": 4857, \"to\": 4865}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While SHEIN's data-driven approach has been a key driver of its success, it has also raised questions about data privacy.\", \"from\": 4867, \"to\": 4988, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"SHEIN's data-driven approach\", \"from\": 4873, \"to\": 4901}, {\"ngram\": \"a key driver\", \"from\": 4911, \"to\": 4923}, {\"ngram\": \"its success\", \"from\": 4927, \"to\": 4938}, {\"ngram\": \"questions\", \"from\": 4959, \"to\": 4968}, {\"ngram\": \"data privacy\", \"from\": 4975, \"to\": 4987}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a company with roots in China, SHEIN's handling of user data has come under scrutiny, particularly in the United States and Europe.\", \"from\": 4989, \"to\": 5123, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5016, \"end\": 5021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999932897481, \"rank\": 6.709656250627792e-09, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 5098, \"end\": 5111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9929687631882844, \"rank\": 0.007081025176896099, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a company\", \"from\": 4992, \"to\": 5001}, {\"ngram\": \"roots\", \"from\": 5007, \"to\": 5012}, {\"ngram\": \"SHEIN's handling\", \"from\": 5023, \"to\": 5039}, {\"ngram\": \"user data\", \"from\": 5043, \"to\": 5052}, {\"ngram\": \"scrutiny\", \"from\": 5068, \"to\": 5076}, {\"ngram\": \"Europe\", \"from\": 5116, \"to\": 5122}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Supply chains for labour-intensive production are shifting from China to countries in Southeast Asia, India, Mexico and Hungary.\", \"from\": 5125, \"to\": 5253, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5189, \"end\": 5194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999932897481, \"rank\": 6.709656250627792e-09, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 5227, \"end\": 5232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9999999999745341, \"rank\": 1.8510809211295046e-11, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}, {\"begin\": 5234, \"end\": 5240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\", \"score\": 0.9999999995452526, \"rank\": 4.4256910982725963e-10, \"text\": \"Mexico\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico\"}, {\"begin\": 5245, \"end\": 5252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.9999992735049911, \"rank\": 6.896281119159525e-07, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Supply chains\", \"from\": 5125, \"to\": 5138}, {\"ngram\": \"labour-intensive production\", \"from\": 5143, \"to\": 5170}, {\"ngram\": \"countries\", \"from\": 5198, \"to\": 5207}, {\"ngram\": \"Southeast Asia\", \"from\": 5211, \"to\": 5225}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The relocation of production has been driven partly by rising costs in China but also by geopolitical tensions between the United States and China, and the proactive efforts of Chinese manufacturers to expand their global presence.\", \"from\": 5254, \"to\": 5485, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5325, \"end\": 5330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999932897481, \"rank\": 6.709656250627792e-09, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 5377, \"end\": 5390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9929687631882844, \"rank\": 0.007081025176896099, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 5395, \"end\": 5400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999932897481, \"rank\": 6.709656250627792e-09, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 5431, \"end\": 5438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999992898358662, \"rank\": 7.100668850017397e-07, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The relocation\", \"from\": 5254, \"to\": 5268}, {\"ngram\": \"production\", \"from\": 5272, \"to\": 5282}, {\"ngram\": \"rising costs\", \"from\": 5309, \"to\": 5321}, {\"ngram\": \"geopolitical tensions\", \"from\": 5343, \"to\": 5364}, {\"ngram\": \"the proactive efforts\", \"from\": 5406, \"to\": 5427}, {\"ngram\": \"their global presence\", \"from\": 5463, \"to\": 5484}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unlike the relocation of capital or information, supply chain shifts involve complex, interdependent actions.\", \"from\": 5487, \"to\": 5596, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the relocation\", \"from\": 5494, \"to\": 5508}, {\"ngram\": \"capital\", \"from\": 5512, \"to\": 5519}, {\"ngram\": \"information\", \"from\": 5523, \"to\": 5534}, {\"ngram\": \"supply chain shifts\", \"from\": 5536, \"to\": 5555}, {\"ngram\": \"complex, interdependent actions\", \"from\": 5564, \"to\": 5595}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Among the different motivations for these shifts, China's manufacturers have to contend with the rise of the China Plus One strategy - a parallel supply chain model.\", \"from\": 5597, \"to\": 5762, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5647, \"end\": 5652, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999932897481, \"rank\": 6.709656250627792e-09, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 5706, \"end\": 5711, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999932897481, \"rank\": 6.709656250627792e-09, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 5712, \"end\": 5720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scratch_Perverts\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 5.710151354255292e-13, \"text\": \"Plus One\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scratch_Perverts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scratch_Perverts\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the different motivations\", \"from\": 5603, \"to\": 5628}, {\"ngram\": \"these shifts\", \"from\": 5633, \"to\": 5645}, {\"ngram\": \"the rise\", \"from\": 5690, \"to\": 5698}, {\"ngram\": \"a parallel supply chain model\", \"from\": 5732, \"to\": 5761}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The growth of these parallel supply chains depends on establishing efficient connections within decentralised networks across national borders, which requires considerable time and effort.\", \"from\": 5763, \"to\": 5951, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The growth\", \"from\": 5763, \"to\": 5773}, {\"ngram\": \"these parallel supply chains\", \"from\": 5777, \"to\": 5805}, {\"ngram\": \"efficient connections\", \"from\": 5830, \"to\": 5851}, {\"ngram\": \"decentralised networks\", \"from\": 5859, \"to\": 5881}, {\"ngram\": \"national borders\", \"from\": 5889, \"to\": 5905}, {\"ngram\": \"considerable time\", \"from\": 5922, \"to\": 5939}, {\"ngram\": \"effort\", \"from\": 5944, \"to\": 5950}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In an interconnected world, the resilience of China's supply chains serves as a reminder of the importance of global specialisation and the need for collaborative efforts to address shared challenges.\", \"from\": 5953, \"to\": 6153, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5999, \"end\": 6004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999932897481, \"rank\": 6.709656250627792e-09, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an interconnected world\", \"from\": 5956, \"to\": 5979}, {\"ngram\": \"the resilience\", \"from\": 5981, \"to\": 5995}, {\"ngram\": \"a reminder\", \"from\": 6031, \"to\": 6041}, {\"ngram\": \"the importance\", \"from\": 6045, \"to\": 6059}, {\"ngram\": \"global specialisation\", \"from\": 6063, \"to\": 6084}, {\"ngram\": \"the need\", \"from\": 6089, \"to\": 6097}, {\"ngram\": \"collaborative efforts\", \"from\": 6102, \"to\": 6123}, {\"ngram\": \"shared challenges\", \"from\": 6135, \"to\": 6152}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just as it is impractical for multinational corporations to entirely exclude Chinese suppliers, China cannot afford to fully localise production, risking the loss of knowledge exchange and capacity upgrading from foreign enterprises.\", \"from\": 6155, \"to\": 6388, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6232, \"end\": 6239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999992898358662, \"rank\": 7.100668850017397e-07, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 6251, \"end\": 6256, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999999932897481, \"rank\": 6.709656250627792e-09, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"multinational corporations\", \"from\": 6185, \"to\": 6211}, {\"ngram\": \"fully localise production\", \"from\": 6274, \"to\": 6299}, {\"ngram\": \"the loss\", \"from\": 6309, \"to\": 6317}, {\"ngram\": \"knowledge exchange\", \"from\": 6321, \"to\": 6339}, {\"ngram\": \"capacity\", \"from\": 6344, \"to\": 6352}, {\"ngram\": \"foreign enterprises\", \"from\": 6368, \"to\": 6387}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As global supply chains evolve, a balanced approach that fosters fair competition, regulates market entry and promotes global standards is essential for sustainable growth and mutually beneficial trade relationships.\", \"from\": 6390, \"to\": 6606, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"global supply chains\", \"from\": 6393, \"to\": 6413}, {\"ngram\": \"a balanced approach\", \"from\": 6422, \"to\": 6441}, {\"ngram\": \"fair competition\", \"from\": 6455, \"to\": 6471}, {\"ngram\": \"market entry\", \"from\": 6483, \"to\": 6495}, {\"ngram\": \"global standards\", \"from\": 6509, \"to\": 6525}, {\"ngram\": \"sustainable growth\", \"from\": 6543, \"to\": 6561}, {\"ngram\": \"mutually beneficial trade relationships\", \"from\": 6566, \"to\": 6605}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Marina Yue Zhang is Associate Professor at the Australia-China Relations Institute, University of Technology Sydney.\", \"from\": 6608, \"to\": 6724, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6615, \"end\": 6618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhejiang\", \"score\": 0.9999999921355993, \"rank\": 7.608494189554123e-09, \"text\": \"Yue\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zhejiang\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zh